OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FFresh west to northwest winds
OL,6,Fbringing showers across the Northeast
OL,7,Ftoday. Outbreaks ranging from quite
OL,8,Ffrequent during the morning and
OL,9,Fscattered for the afternoon, with
OL,10,FDeeside seeing the best of the shelter
OL,11,Fand limited brighter spells.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA rather cloudy evening with
OL,14,Ffurther showers, these focused across
OL,15,Fthe north. Clear spells developing
OL,16,Fovernight, particularly across
OL,17,Fsouthern areas where showers largely
OL,18,Fdie out.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
