OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FMany enjoying a dry day with
OL,6,Flight winds and good sunny spells
OL,7,Fdeveloping into the afternoon.
OL,8,FHowever, some early light showers will
OL,9,Fappear, chiefly confined to the north.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMost
OL,12,Fdry during Monday, with sunshine
OL,13,Fturning hazy for the afternoon.
OL,14,FHowever, occasional areas of rain
OL,15,Fcrossing the area from the southwest
OL,16,Ffrom late Monday and through Tuesday
OL,17,Fand Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
